{"tid":1808892,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"唔好再叫「香港警察」做黑警","createTime":"2020-01-02T16:15:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-02T21:20:41.000Z","uid":276533,"like":50,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"98e8e927ba5320644aca771dc357550960b268fd","tid":1808892,"uid":276533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T16:15:54.000Z","msg":"因為佢哋係恐怖份子<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wy4N8Ok.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWy4N8Ok.jpg&h=4e862e8c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n其實<strong>香港警察一早已經停止存在</strong>，佢哋現在每一個行為，已經可以歸類為<strong>恐怖主義</strong>。<br />\n叫佢哋做「黑警」，係濫用咗「警察」嘅意思，亦暗示咗仲有白警嘅存在。<br />\n所以我哋<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>唔需要浪費時間反駁或者恥笑佢哋記者會講嘅嘢</strong></span>。外國傳媒根本都唔會直播或者反駁阿蓋達，伊斯蘭國嘅記者會。<br />\n而家一定要做心理上嘅改變，唔好再承認香港警察嘅存在，只有<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">自稱「香港警察」嘅恐怖份子和有組織犯罪集團</span></span></strong>。<br />\n係文宣同埋國際戰線，應該幫佢哋加引號：<span style=\"color: blue;\">自稱「香港警察」的犯罪集團／恐怖組織 (the so-called &quot;Hong Kong Police Force&quot; terrorist organization)</span><br />\n不要說「<span style=\"color: red;\">襲警</span>」，試著說「<span style=\"color: orange;\">打擊恐怖主義</span>」；不要說「<span style=\"color: red;\">被捕</span>」，試著說「<span style=\"color: orange;\">被挾持</span>」。<br />\n所有撐警人士，一律淪為支持恐怖主義者。所有「警隊」嘅人員，無論係文員，鑑證，軍裝，防暴，無論角色如何，都係恐怖集團嘅其中一員，必須被消滅。<br />\n我哋咁樣先可以跨過嘅而家嘅<strong>心理關口</strong>。義士嘅意思，就係為打擊恐怖主義而犧牲嘅人。<strong><em>光復香港，其中一個任務就係反恐。</em></strong>"},{"pid":"bef3ce5027735b5a04998f49410c055e6a6058ca","tid":1808892,"uid":276533,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T16:18:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BRQ9CVQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBRQ9CVQ.jpg&h=850f1143&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2a62b00850997d1d69a7aae2a23bf77931572b8a","tid":1808892,"uid":48974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T16:20:07.000Z","msg":"恐怖分子"},{"pid":"3c76e797d167af512d9bfe9906fa37c61df205ca","tid":1808892,"uid":229920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T16:21:01.000Z","msg":"恐怖分子死全家"},{"pid":"292abfa0fd511d2448526d3c8cd14485c6abda37","tid":1808892,"uid":273593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T16:21:45.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"bca08bab3ef935a397021013da225968b3da989d","tid":1808892,"uid":28181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T16:22:11.000Z","msg":"正名好重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"439831161c48d70ffb96d556a8947ce8faacf874","tid":1808892,"uid":204929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T16:22:53.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f8e2a61a4e50874d4b331f117718612a3c9aa062","tid":1808892,"uid":28181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T16:23:27.000Z","msg":"有識人做恐佈分子一定要日講夜講佢地做恐佈分子~"},{"pid":"e1071c0deb21e21f07dcbda78280bc996556e657","tid":1808892,"uid":152815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T16:26:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e12646201f6bba87603d8caa9c9ffc4679289719","tid":1808892,"uid":188685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T16:26:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1.3 教育界愛丁堡<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8eGQm65.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8eGQm65.jpg&h=9739b00d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">*不捉鬼<br />\n屌狗一時爽 勇武少一人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n加入工會 全民三罷<br />\n⚠️工會大全⚠️<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/hkonstrike/663\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkonstrike%2F663&d=lD%2FUaJpd7HswZ4lFnFCcPkVeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=32cad50e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/hkonstrike/663</a><br />\n<br />\n⚠️Group List⚠️<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/hkonstrike/669\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/l